high_descs: Turn right and stop at the right of the toilet
Grab the candle from the top of the toilet
Go to the sink and back up and look at the cabinets at the bottom
Put the candle in the second cabinet from the right
Move forward to the sink
Grab the candle that is to the right of the sink
Back up from the sink and face the bottom
Put the candle in the second cabinet from the right
anns.task_desc: Putting two candles in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the candle off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right again and walk forward, turn around to face the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the right below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the cabinet door.
Walk up to the counter.
Pick up the candle to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn back around to face the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the right below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into a cabinet.

high_descs: move a few steps to the right
pick up the candle that on the back of the toilet
turn right, walk to the wall, turn left to face sink
open cabinet under the sink, put candle in cabinet, close cabinet
walk forward to sink
pick up the candle that is on the counter to the right of the sink
move two steps back
open cabinet under the sink, put candle in cabinet, close cabinet
anns.task_desc: put two candles under the sink
